msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"- Quantized model `glm-5-w4a8` and `glm-5.1-w4a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas"
" 800 A3 (64G × 16) ."
msgstr ""
"- 量化模型 `glm-5-w4a8` 和 `glm-5.1-w4a8` 可部署在 1 台 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）上。"

msgid ""
"- Quantized model `glm-5-w8a8` and `glm-5.1-w8a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas"
" 800 A3 (64G × 16) ."
msgstr ""
"- 量化模型 `glm-5-w8a8` 和 `glm-5.1-w8a8` 可部署在 1 台 Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）上。"

msgid ""
"- Quantized model `glm-5-w4a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) ."
msgstr "- 量化模型 `glm-5-w4a8` 可部署在 1 台 Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）上。"

msgid ""
"**Notice:**\n"
"The parameters are explained as follows:"
msgstr ""
"**注意：**\n"
"参数说明如下："

msgid ""
