msgstr "- 对于单节点部署，在低延迟场景下，建议使用 `dp1tp16` 并关闭专家并行。"

msgid "### 5.2 Multi-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.2 多节点部署"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to verify multi-node "
