msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: The following configurations are validated in specific test "
"environments and are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends "
"on factors such as maximum input/output length, prefix cache hit rate, "
"precision requirements, and deployment machine ratios. It is recommended to "
"refer to Section 9.2 for tuning based on actual conditions."
msgstr ""
"> **注意**：以下配置在特定测试环境中经过验证，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于最大输入/输出长度、前缀缓存命中率、精度要求和部署机器比例等因素。建议参考第"
" 9.2 节根据实际情况进行调优。"

msgid "#### Table 1: Scenario Overview"
msgstr "#### 表 1：场景概览"

msgid ""
"|Scenario|Deployment Mode|*Total NPUs|Weight Version|Key Considerations|\n"
"|--------|---------------|-----------|---------------|-------------------|\n"
"|High Throughput|1P1D deployment|32 (A3)|GLM5-w8a8/GLM5.1-w8a8|dp4 tp8 on P nodes and dp8 dp4 on D nodes to balanced latency and throughput|\n"
"|Low Latency|1P1D deployment|32 (A3)|GLM5-w8a8/GLM5.1-w8a8|dp4 tp8 on both P and D nodes to reduce latency|"
msgstr ""
"|场景|部署模式|*NPU总数|权重版本|关键考量|\n"
"|--------|---------------|-----------|---------------|-------------------|\n"
"|高吞吐量|1P1D 部署|32 (A3)|GLM5-w8a8/GLM5.1-w8a8|P 节点上 dp4 tp8，D 节点上 dp8 dp4，以平衡延迟和吞吐量|\n"
"|低延迟|1P1D 部署|32 (A3)|GLM5-w8a8/GLM5.1-w8a8|P 和 D 节点上均使用 dp4 tp8，以降低延迟|"

msgid ""
"> `*Total NPUs` indicates the total number of NPUs used across all nodes."
msgstr "> `*NPU总数` 表示所有节点上使用的 NPU 总数。"

msgid "#### Table 2: Detailed Node Configuration"
msgstr "#### 表 2：详细节点配置"

msgid ""
"|Scenario|Configuration|NPUs|TP|DP|Max Num Seqs|Max Num Batched Tokens|Max Model Len|MTP Speculation Num|\n"
"|--------|-------------|-----|--|--|------------|----------------------|--------------|--------------------|\n"
"|High Throughput (A3)|1P1D deployment|32|P:8 D:4|P:4 D:8|P:64 D:128|P:4096 D:32|P:133120 D:150000|3|\n"
"|Low Latency (A3)|1P1D deployment|32|4|8|P:64 D:128|P:4096 D:32|P:133120 D:150000|3|"
msgstr ""
"|场景|配置|NPU|TP|DP|最大序列数|最大批处理 Token 数|最大模型长度|MTP 推测数量|\n"
"|--------|-------------|-----|--|--|------------|----------------------|--------------|--------------------|\n"
"|高吞吐量 (A3)|1P1D 部署|32|P:8 D:4|P:4 D:8|P:64 D:128|P:4096 D:32|P:133120 D:150000|3|\n"
"|低延迟 (A3)|1P1D 部署|32|4|8|P:64 D:128|P:4096 D:32|P:133120 D:150000|3|"

